<h1 class="article">MAGAphobia Watch: Oklahoma Teen Bullies Student Over MAGA Flag, Hat</h1> <p class="byline">
Posted at 9:00 am on February 27, 2019 by <a href="/sister-toldjah">Sister Toldjah</a>
</p>
<div class="row button-span">
<div class="col-xs-9">
<div class="row">
